7 An Act relating to higher education; amending 70 O.S.
2021, Section 3231, which relates to the Oklahoma
8 National Guard Educational Assistance Act; including
program fees; requiring joint approval of fees;
9 authorizing cap; requiring certain specialty to
retain eligibility; authorizing Military Department
